name: Expanding Heads: Screen (Part 1 of 3)
description: The first of 3 pieces in a series of ever-expanding heads. A 4th piece will be available exclusively to those who manage to collect all 3. These will be released on a weekly basis. Sound design by Mindwipe (https://soundcloud.com/mindwipebeats). DM me on Twitter at siegmattel to claim your winning.
